section*
  type admissionevaluation
  code $loinc#67852-4 Hospital Admission evaluation note
  title Admission evaluation
  text """Mr. Luigi De Luca, a 57-year-old male, was admitted on 1st April following a pre-diabetic episode characterized by episodes of fatigue, polyuria, and increased thirst. Recent routine blood tests showed elevated fasting blood glucose and HbA1c levels that required further investigation.<p/>When Mr De Luca arrived in the morning we recorded a fasting blood glucose level at 180 mg/dL. His HbA1c level was 7.8%. He seemed to be dehydrated, so that he immediately was sent to the ward for a full breakfast and fluid substitution."""
