  text """During the hospital stay from 1 to 10 April, Mr. De Luca underwent a series of diagnostic tests, consultations and initial treatment. <p/>Throughout his hospital stay, Mr. De Luca was monitored closely. His blood sugar levels improved modestly with the introduction of Metformin, and no acute complications were observed."""
